[src:adam-optimizer/stochastic-gradient-descent] As an example, consider least squares with features $x_{1},\ldots ,x_{n}\in \mathbb {R} ^{p}$ and observations $y_{1},\ldots ,y_{n}\in \mathbb {R}$ .
